/-- **Tight heat-smoothed strain ŠłĘňĘ sum bound.** Summing the two tight
strain ŠłĘňĘ bounds:

    `‚ÄĖe^{tőĒ}S‚āÄ‚āÄ‚ÄĖ¬≤_{ŠłĘňĘ} + ‚ÄĖe^{tőĒ}S‚āÄ‚āĀ‚ÄĖ¬≤_{ŠłĘňĘ} ‚Č§ ‚ÄĖőł‚ÄĖ¬≤_{ŠłĘ^{s+1}} / 2`

The factor 1/2 reflects the strain-Frobenius tight identity
`ő£‚ÄĖS_ij‚ÄĖ¬≤ = ‚ÄĖn‚ÄĖ¬≤/2` (and the heat contraction keeps the bound). -/
theorem heat_smoothed_sqgStrain_Hs_sum_le (s : ‚ĄĚ) {t : ‚ĄĚ} (ht : 0 ‚Č§ t)
    (őł S00 S01 : Lp ‚Ąā 2 (volume : Measure (UnitAddTorus (Fin 2))))
    (hcoeff0 : ‚ąÄ n, mFourierCoeff S00 n =
      ((heatSymbol t n : ‚ĄĚ) : ‚Ąā) * sqgStrainSymbol 0 0 n * mFourierCoeff őł n)
    (hcoeff1 : ‚ąÄ n, mFourierCoeff S01 n =
      ((heatSymbol t n : ‚ĄĚ) : ‚Ąā) * sqgStrainSymbol 0 1 n * mFourierCoeff őł n)
    (hsum : Summable
