Composes ¬ß10.157's `fourierSynthesisLp` with an `lp`-valued per-mode
limit `bLp : ‚ĄĚ ‚Üí lp (fun _ => ‚Ąā) 2` into the concrete
`őł_lim : ‚ĄĚ ‚Üí Lp ‚Ąā 2` operator required by `HasFourierSynthesis.ofPerModeLimit`
