/-! ### ¬ß10.169 Theorem 3 on the Aubin‚ÄďLions limit

Capstone composing ¬ß10.167 + ¬ß10.168 + ¬ß10.7's
`sqg_regularity_via_s2_bootstrap` into a single theorem: conditional
Theorem 3 on `s ‚ąą [0, 2]` for the `L¬≤`-limit of a Galerkin sequence
with uniform `ŠłĘňĘ` control across `s ‚ąą [1, 2]`.

This is the **maximally-closed form** of the conditional Theorem 3
reachable from the current infrastructure: the hypotheses are exactly
the uniform `ŠłĘňĘ` bounds on the Galerkin approximation (which classical
Galerkin energy theory supplies).  No finite-support assumption on
`őł_lim`; no axiom beyond mathlib. -/

/-- **¬ß10.169  Theorem 3 on `s ‚ąą [0, 2]` for the Aubin‚ÄďLions limit.**

Composes:

* ¬ß10.167.C `MaterialMaxPrinciple.of_aubinLions_uniform_H1` ‚ÄĒ MMP
  from uniform `ŠłĘ¬Ļ` bound on Galerkin states.
* ¬ß10.168.B `BKMCriterionS2.of_aubinLions_uniform_Hs` ‚ÄĒ BKM from
  uniform `ŠłĘňĘ` bound on Galerkin states at every `s ‚ąą (1, 2]`.
* `sqg_regularity_via_s2_bootstrap` ‚ÄĒ MMP + BKM ‚áí uniform `ŠłĘňĘ`
  bound on `s ‚ąą [0, 2]`.

Produces: for every `s ‚ąą [0, 2]`, a uniform bound
`hsSeminormSq s (ext.őł_lim t) ‚Č§ M'` at every `t ‚Č• 0`.

The caller supplies `M‚āĀ` and `Ms : ‚ĄĚ ‚Üí ‚ĄĚ` (the `ŠłĘ¬Ļ` and per-`s`
`ŠłĘňĘ` bounds on the Galerkin approximation).  These are the **only**
hypotheses required: there is no finite-support restriction on
`őł_lim`, no `DecidableEq` binder, and no appeal to any analytic axiom
outside `sqg_regularity_via_s2_bootstrap`. -/
theorem sqg_regularity_of_aubinLions_uniform_Hs
    {őł : Lp ‚Ąā 2 (volume : Measure (UnitAddTorus (Fin 2)))}
    {őĪ : ‚ąÄ n : ‚Ąē, ‚ĄĚ ‚Üí (‚Ü•(sqgBox n) ‚Üí ‚Ąā)}
    (ext : HasAubinLionsExtraction őł őĪ)
    (M‚āĀ : ‚ĄĚ) (Ms : ‚ĄĚ ‚Üí ‚ĄĚ)
    (hBoundOne : ‚ąÄ n : ‚Ąē, ‚ąÄ t : ‚ĄĚ, 0 ‚Č§ t ‚Üí
      hsSeminormSq 1 (galerkinToLp (sqgBox n) (őĪ n t)) ‚Č§ M‚āĀ)
    (hBoundS : ‚ąÄ n : ‚Ąē, ‚ąÄ t : ‚ĄĚ, 0 ‚Č§ t ‚Üí ‚ąÄ s : ‚ĄĚ, 1 < s ‚Üí s ‚Č§ 2 ‚Üí
      hsSeminormSq s (galerkinToLp (sqgBox n) (őĪ n t)) ‚Č§ Ms s) :
    ‚ąÄ s : ‚ĄĚ, 0 ‚Č§ s ‚Üí s ‚Č§ 2 ‚Üí
      ‚ąÉ M' : ‚ĄĚ, ‚ąÄ t : ‚ĄĚ, 0 ‚Č§ t ‚Üí hsSeminormSq s (ext.őł_lim t) ‚Č§ M' :=
  sqg_regularity_via_s2_bootstrap ext.őł_lim
    (MaterialMaxPrinciple.of_aubinLions_uniform_H1 ext M‚āĀ hBoundOne)
    (BKMCriterionS2.of_aubinLions_uniform_Hs ext Ms hBoundS)

/-! ### ¬ß10.170 Zero-datum instance of ¬ß10.169

