/-! ### ¬ß10.172 Item 1 structural closure via pointwise `galerkinRHS`
bound + `L¬≤` conservation (bypasses `hH2`)

Closes the `hH2` (uniform `H‚ĀĽ¬≤` bound on `galerkinRHS`) analytic input
of Item 1 **unconditionally** from Galerkin `L¬≤` conservation (¬ß10.97).
Uses only the pointwise Fourier-side estimate

    `‚ÄĖgalerkinRHS S (galerkinExtend S c) m‚ÄĖ ‚Č§ latticeNorm m ¬∑ ‚ąĎ_{n ‚ąą S} ‚ÄĖc n‚ÄĖ¬≤`

derived from:

