Combined with ¬ß10.97 `L¬≤` conservation:
`‚ąĎ_{m ‚ąą sqgBox n} ‚ÄĖőĪ n ŌĄ m‚ÄĖ¬≤ ‚Č§ ‚ÄĖőł‚āÄ‚ÄĖ¬≤_{L¬≤}` uniformly, and with ¬ß10.153.B
mean-value theorem on per-mode trajectories, this delivers a per-mode
