/-- **¬ß12 ‚ÄĒ End-to-end capstone: `SqgEvolutionAxioms_strong` from the
classical weak form.**

Composition of `of_testFormWeakSolution` with
`SqgEvolutionAxioms_strong.of_IsSqgWeakSolution_via_MMP`. Any
